user should be able to :
    save, edit, remove a transaction (debit | credit)
    save, edit, remove periodic transaction (debit | credit)

    list upcoming debit transaction
    list upcoming credit transaction

    import, export transactions

    add category to transaction (fd, rd, mf, stock, stock_dividend, mf_dividend, food, groceries,....)
    attach category to category_group

    specify transaction mode to keep track of where/how transaction was performed
    (upi, cash , online, debitcard, creditcard, paytm, gpay, amazonpay, phonepay)

    generate spend analytics (monthly, yearly, categorized)